<PageLayout>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-600">
        These terms govern your use of SalesTag services. We've written them in plain English to make sure you understand your rights and responsibilities when using our platform.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          By using SalesTag, you agree to these terms. We provide conversation recording, analysis, and coaching tools for sales teams. Our goal is to help you improve performance while maintaining the highest standards of privacy and ethics.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Use SalesTag responsibly and legally. Record conversations only with proper consent and in compliance with local laws. Don't use our platform for harassment, deception, or any activity that violates regulations or harms others.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Account Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          You're responsible for keeping your account secure and for all activity under your account. Use strong passwords, don't share credentials, and notify us immediately if you suspect unauthorized access.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Service Availability</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We work hard to keep SalesTag available 24/7, but we can't guarantee 100% uptime. We'll provide reasonable notice for planned maintenance and work quickly to resolve any unexpected issues.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          SalesTag is a tool to help improve sales performance, but ultimate responsibility for your sales results and compliance with regulations remains with you. We're not liable for business outcomes or regulatory violations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction where SalesTag operates. Any disputes will be resolved through binding arbitration rather than court proceedings, keeping resolution efficient and cost-effective.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
